<p><font size="4" face="Georgia">отсюда </font></p>
<p align="center" style="text-align:center">
<span style="position: relative; top: 5.0pt"><font size="4" face="Georgia"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape
 id="_x0000_s1026" type="#_x0000_t75" style='width:101.25pt;height:24pt'>
